  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "ルイス・キャロルの『不思議の国のアリス』を基にした『不思議の夢のアリス』は、かわいらしい2Dプラットフォーマーで、あなたはピンクのドレスを着た金髪の少女アリスを操作します。あなたの仕事は、森や洞窟を進みながら出会う敵を、頭にジャンプするか「イヤ！」と叫ぶことで倒すことです。いくつかの敵は爆発する卵を落とします。これらの卵を蹴って、敵を自分で破壊することができます。各エリアには3つのレベルがあり、各レベルの最後にはボスを倒すことになります。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "A platformer from FACE inspired by Alice in Wonderland.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Based on Lewis Carrol's Alice in Wonderland novels, Fushigi no Yume no Alice is a cute 2-D platformer which casts you as Alice, a blond-haired girl wearing a pink dress. Your job is to make your way through forests and caves, defeating enemies that you come across by either jumping on their heads or shouting 'IYA' at them. Some enemies will drop eggs which will explode. You can kick these eggs and use them to destroy the enemies themselves. There are three levels in each area, and each level ends with you defeating a boss.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ],
